headline: HeartCore Enterprises, Inc. (HTCR) Reports Q4 Loss, Misses Revenue Estimates
summary: HeartCore Enterprises (HTCR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -525% and 27.19%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
